These last two posts of yours were quite confusing, Tim. You did not state who you were replying to or quote any text. I gather that you were replying to me because of the content of your posts, but even that is a guess I don't put much stake in. Some of your points are seemingly irrelevant to points I have made or are related only minimally. Please do try to make yourself more understandable.<br>
<br>
And you still haven't answered my first question: Who are these people? What data have they exaggerated or falsified?  <p>--<br>
